Mapping meta::relational::tests::mapping::extend::storeSubstitution::AMapping
(   
   A[a] : Relational
   {
      id : [testDatabase]ABC.id,
      aName : [testDatabase]ABC.aName
   }
)

Mapping meta::relational::tests::mapping::extend::storeSubstitution::BMapping
